{UTF-8}
Correction Rate=DELAY FIXED(Viral Spread Rate, Verification Lag, 0)
	~	People/Hr
	~		|

Debunking Rate=People Believing Fake News * (People Reached by Fact Check / 10000)
	~	People/Hour
	~		|

People Believing Fake News= INTEG (Viral Spread Rate-Debunking Rate,
		10)
	~	People
	~		|

People Reached by Fact Check= INTEG (Correction Rate,
		0)
	~	People
	~		|

Sensationalism Factor=1.5
	~	Dmnl
	~		|

Verification Lag=4
	~	Hour
	~		|

Viral Spread Rate=(People Reached by Fact Check * 0.2) * Sensationalism Factor
	~	People/Hour
	~		|

********************************************************
	.Control
********************************************************~
		Simulation Control Parameters
	|

FINAL TIME  = 72
	~	Hour
	~	The final time for the simulation.
	|

INITIAL TIME  = 0
	~	Hour
	~	The initial time for the simulation.
	|

SAVEPER  = 
        TIME STEP 
	~	Hour [0,?]
	~	The frequency with which output is stored.
	|

TIME STEP  = 0.5
	~	Hour [0,?]
	~	The time step for the simulation.
	|

